data.description: Provides detailed examination of careers in Human Ecology and the fields of human development and family studies (HDFS). High level leaders working in a variety of professions related to the HDFS major will present as guest speakers (e.g., counseling, school psychology, family life education, early childhood education, child life, social work, health care, occupational therapy).
data.title: HUMAN DEVELOPMENT & FAMILY STUDIES LEADERSHIP SYMPOSIUM
